==English==

===Expression===
'''[[excuse]] [[me]]'''

# ''Said as a request to repeat information.''
# ''Said as a request for an individual's attention.''
# ''Said as a request to pass.''
# [[sorry|Sorry]], as an apology.
# ''Said as a request for an apology.''

